==Twin towns – sister cities==

Liepāja is twinned with:

* Nynäshamn, Sweden (1990)
* Elbląg, Poland (1991)
* Bellevue, United States (1992)
* Darmstadt, Germany (1993)
* Klaipėda, Lithuania (1997)
* Gdynia, Poland (1999)
* Årstad (Bergen), Norway (2001)
* Palanga, Lithuania (2001)
* Helsingborg, Sweden (2005)
* Guldborgsund, Denmark
